ctly goes to the US and bypass the Chinese Great Firewall.<br />\nInteresting as the website netdna.com is slower (although they use their own cdn) with some gif appearing one after the other compare to MaxCDN opening like a rocket (seems they don''t use CDN).<br />\nConcerning my site, it still loads quicker with the CDN switched off. Strange (?) Must keep on studying this....</p>\n<p>Anyway we can close this topic as the problem of uploading files out of the WP Media Library has been solved.<br />\nA BIG THANKS TO Frederick Townes for his precious tip!\n</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/9hegpuU2AYM" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:101:"http://wordpress.org/support/topic/plugin-w3-total-cache-alternative-to-wp-media-library#post-1745164";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:2:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"Steve Jennings on "wp-admin White Screen W3TC and Redirection Conflict"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:110:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/ooOMyeDZXCM/wp-admin-white-screen-w3tc-and-redirection-conflict";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:29:"Mon, 18 Oct 2010 09:08:35 PDT";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:37:"1745156@http://wordpress.org/support/";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";