ttp://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";s:5:"slash";s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";s:5:"media";s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";}}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:345:"Missed the news last week or so, but Twitter added oEmbed provider support to their API. While previous methods have existed to easily post tweets (such as Blackbird Pie), oEmbed is built into the WordPress core. However, since Twitter didn&#8217;t implement oEmbed discovery, and WP has discovery off by default anyway, you have to resort [...]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"xmlns";a:7:{s:7:"content";s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";s:3:"wfw";s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";s:2:"dc";s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";s:4:"atom";s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";s:2:"sy";s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";s:5:"slash";s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";s:5:"media";s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";}}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Otto";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"xmlns";a:7:{s:7:"content";s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";s:3:"wfw";s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";s:2:"dc";s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";s:4:"atom";s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";s:2:"sy";s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";s:5:"slash";s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";s:5:"media";s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";}}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:2903:"<fb:like href=''http://ottopress.com/2011/twitter-adds-oembed-adding-it-to-wordpress-with-a-snippet/'' send=''true'' layout=''standard'' show_faces=''true'' width=''450'' height=''65'' action=''recommend'' colorscheme=''light'' font=''lucida+grande''></fb:like><p>Missed the news last week or so, but Twitter added oEmbed provider support to their API. While previous methods have existed to easily post tweets (such as Blackbird Pie), oEmbed is built into the WordPress core.</p>\n<p>However, since Twitter didn&#8217;t implement oEmbed discovery, and WP has discovery off by default anyway, you have to resort to a small bit of code to make it work. Here&#8217;s that bit of code:</p>\n<pre class="brush: php; notranslate">\nadd_filter(''oembed_providers'',''twitter_oembed'');\nfunction twitter_oembed($a) {\n	$a[''#http(s)?://(www\\.)?twitter.com/.+?/status(es)?/.*#i''] = array( ''http://api.twitter.com/1/statuses/oembed.{format}'', true);\n	return $a;\n}\n</pre>\n<p>Here&#8217;s what happens when you put that code in a plugin (for example) and just paste a twitter URL into a post:</p>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-in-reply-to="149233976605818881" width="550"><p>@<a href="https://twitter.com/Otto42">Otto42</a> Led Zeppelin can <img src=''http://ottopress.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif'' alt='':P'' class=''wp-smiley'' />  RT @<a href="https://twitter.com/Otto42">Otto42</a> Even Google knows that one does not simply walk into Mordor.</p>\n<p>&mdash; Dresden Diaz (@DieselFlowers) <a href="https://twitter.com/DieselFlowers/status/149288982168092674" data-datetime="2011-12-21T00:44:01+00:00">December 21, 2011</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>\n<p>It handles RT&#8217;s pretty neatly, I think. <img src=''http://ottopress.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif'' alt='':)'' class=''wp-smiley'' /> </p>\n<p>This may make it into WordPress by default in <a href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/19626">the next version</a>. Too bad they came out with it too late for inclusion in WordPress 3.3. </p>\n<a href=''http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fotto42.com%2Fb1&count=vertical&related=otto42%2Cottodestruct&text=Twitter adds oEmbed - Adding it to WordPress with a snippet'' class=''twitter-share-button'' data-text=''Twitter adds oEmbed - Adding it to WordPress with a snippet'' data-url=''http://otto42.com/b1'' data-counturl=''http://ottopress.com/2011/twitter-adds-oembed-adding-it-to-wordpress-with-a-snippet/'' data-count=''vertical'' data-via=''ottodestruct'' data-related=''otto42,ottodestruct''></a><span class="fb_share"><fb:like href="http://ottopress.com/2011/twitter-adds-oembed-adding-it-to-wordpress-with-a-snippet/" layout="box_count"></fb:like></span><div class="plusone"><g:plusone size=tall annotation=bubble align=left href="http://ottopress.com/2011/twitter-adds-oembed-adding-it-to-wordpress-with-a-snippet/"></g:plusone></div>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"xmlns";a:7:{s:7:"content";s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";s:3:"wfw";s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";s:2:"dc";s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";s:4:"atom";s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";s:2:"sy";s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";s:5:"slash";s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";s:5:"media";s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";}}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:89:"http://ottopress.com/2011/twitter-adds-oembed-adding-it-to-wordpress-with-a-snippet/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"xmlns";a:7:{s:7:"content";s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";s:3:"wfw";s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";s:2:"dc";s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";s:4:"atom";s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";s:2:"sy";s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";s:5:"slash";s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";s:5:"media";s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";}}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:2:"16";s:7:"attribs";a: