(52, 1, '2009-06-07 16:53:51', '2009-06-07 04:53:51', '<p>Urban Legend web is a sole trader web design and development shop. </p>\r\n<p>We specialise in websites for small to medium sized businesses. Our focus on&nbsp; <strong>web standards</strong> and best practice coding means that not only will your site load fast, look good, and be easy to change, it will be more <strong>prominent</strong> in <strong>search engines</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>We''re well versed in content management systems, and apart from coding our own simple systems, have worked with Wordpress, osCommerce, and in-house commercial systems.</p>\r\n<p>And of course, being small, you''ll reap the benefits of low overheads, and a personal touch.</p>\r\n<p>So contact us today for a no-obligation quote on your new website.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'About', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-6', '', '', '2009-06-07 16:53:51', '2009-06-07 04:53:51', '', 2, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/06/2-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
