(538, 1, '2010-10-19 11:03:27', '2010-10-18 23:03:27', '<p>This site, <a title="The Designers Library - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://thedesignerslibrary.co.nz"> The Designers Library</a>, is for a soft-furnishings (&nbsp;curtains , blinds etc ) company in Hamilton, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>It is designed by <a title="CubeMedia - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.box.co.nz/">CubeMedia</a>, and converted into a fully-functional Wordpress - powered website by Urban Legend Web.</p>\r\n<p>It uses a JQuery - based slider for the slideshow on the front page, and a semi-transparent background for the centered content area. A&nbsp;combination of native Wordpress abilities, plugins, and customised templates drive the site.</p>', 'The Designers Library', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'the-designers-library', '', '', '2012-01-21 14:00:07', '2012-01-21 02:00:07', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/?p=538', 0, 'post', '', 0),
