(116, 1, '2009-09-10 23:28:51', '2009-09-10 11:28:51', '<p>This site is for a plastering contract company covering the Bay of Plenty and Waikato areas.</p>\r\n<p>It uses flash animation, as well as an image gallery, to showcase some of the company''s work.</p>\r\n<p>The site is built using the Wordpress engine, and the design is by Urban Legend web, based on the <a target="_blank" title="visit the theme author''s site - opens in new window" href="http://themes.jestro.com/titan/">Titan theme</a>.</p>', 'Lumena Plaster', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'lumena-plaster', '', '', '2012-01-21 14:03:07', '2012-01-21 02:03:07', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/?p=116', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(142, 1, '2009-10-04 13:28:41', '2009-10-04 01:28:41', '<p>This site is for an Auckland art gallery, and is designed by Helen Smith of <a title="McGovern &amp; Associates - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.mcgovern.co.nz/">McGovern &amp; Associates</a>. Its layout, including top-level subsections, is coded by Urban Legend web. It uses McGovern''s content management system to allow the client to enter and edit content.</p>', 'John Leech Gallery', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'john-leech-gallery', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:24:11', '2012-01-16 01:24:11', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/?p=142', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(145, 1, '2009-10-04 13:49:10', '2009-10-04 01:49:10', '<p>This site is for a top Auckland photographer who was the official photographer for the Dalai Lama of Tibet on his last visit to these shores.</p>\r\n<p>Its design, by Urban Legend web, is intended to take a back seat to the photgraphs, many of which are stunning. It features a gallery of images sorted by subject, with a custom-built engine written in PHP.</p>\r\n<p>As is standard practice at Urban Legend web, It is coded to <a target="newone" title="visit The Web Standards Project - opens in new window" href="http://www.webstandards.org/">web standards</a> using valid XHTML and CSS</p>', 'Jacqui Walker, Photographer', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'jacqui-walker-photographer', '', '', '2012-01-16 22:30:38', '2012-01-16 10:30:38', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/?p=145', 0, 'post', '', 0),
