(158, 1, '2009-07-08 00:25:15', '2009-07-07 12:25:15', '<p>We offer a range of services, from simple cookie-cutter brochure-type static web sites to&nbsp; custom-designed fully-functional e-commerce site.</p>\r\n<p>We also offer website coding services, search engine optimisation, website face-lifts, and website code over-hauls.</p>\r\n<p>For new sites, we''d like to offer some hard-and-fast quotes, but there are so many variables that that''s almost impossible to do. </p>\r\n<p>Below are some starting points, but you can always <a href="/contact/" title="Contact Us">contact us</a>, tell us what you want, and we''ll send you an obligation-free quote for your new website. </p>\r\n<h3>From $350</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Brochure-type website</li>\r\n    <li>Designed from a choice of high-quality templates</li>\r\n    <li>Up to 4 pages including a contact page and gallery</li>\r\n    <li>Basic search-engine submission</li>\r\n    <li>Updates are charged by Urban Legend Web at a reasonable rate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>From $600</h3>\r\n<p>All of the above, but with an <strong>original, custom design</strong>, and up to 5 pages. </p>\r\n<h3>From $900</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Dynamic website</li>\r\n    <li>Using a <strong>content management system</strong> which allows you, the site owner, to update the site. That includes editing page text, updating image galleries, and more. </li>\r\n    <li>Original, custom design</li>\r\n    <li>Unlimited pages</li>\r\n    <li>Email subscription service</li>\r\n    <li>Search engine optimisation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>From $1200</h3>\r\n<p>All of the above but with other more complex options, which may involve forums, secure areas of the website, or other customisations. Any and all extras you can think of. <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a> to find out more.</p>\r\n<h3><a name="coding">Website Coding</a></h3>\r\n<p>Urban Legend Web has for some years now worked on a contract basis for McGovern &amp;&nbsp;Associates, a top Auckland web shop, and others. We''re experts at cutting and coding websites using modern methods.</p>\r\n<h3>Search Engine Optimisation</h3>\r\n<p>Have you got a website which is sitting there idle, unknown to the rest of the world?&nbsp;It may be fully functional in all other aspects, but unless it attracts visitors, you may as well not have bothered. We can help in using legitimate methods to drive more search engine traffic to your website.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Code Overhauls</h3>\r\n<p>The web is littered with sites coded using out-dated methods. These websites can be stream-lined to load more quickly, display more reliably, and be more easily updated.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Face-lifts</h3>\r\n<p>Do you have a site which looks like it was designed in the previous millenium?&nbsp; Perhaps it was. They say content is king, but visitors are much less likely to explore a web-site which is unattractively designed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Services', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '90-revision-7', '', '', '2009-07-08 00:25:15', '2009-07-07 12:25:15', '', 90, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2009/07/90-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(89, 1, '2009-06-10 01:17:09', '2009-06-09 13:17:09', '<p>As the page name implies, this is the first post in what will be an occasional blog.</p>\r\n<p>I''ll concentrate on issues revolving around web design and development, especially as it relates to website owners, rather than website developers.</p>\r\n<p>Here I''ll post some tips and tricks for non-specialist website content managers - i.e. those who want to update their own sites.</p>\r\n<p>This site itself, and clients'' sites - not all, of course - are built on the Wordpress engine, so it makes sense for the above-named tips to lean toward working with Wordpress.</p>\r\n<p>Check back here for updates.</p>', 'Hello !', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-5', '', '', '2009-06-10 01:17:09', '2009-06-09 13:17:09', '', 33, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/06/33-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(90, 1, '2009-06-12 22:52:07', '2009-06-12 10:52:07', '<h3><a name="coding">Website Coding</a></h3>\r\n<p>Urban Legend Web has for some years now worked on a contract basis for <a href="http://www.mcgovern.co.nz">McGovern &amp;&nbsp;Associates</a>, a top Auckland web shop, and others. We''re experts at cutting and coding websites using modern methods.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Content Management Systems</h3>\r\n<p><img alt="wordpress" title="wordpress" width="138" height="96" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-848" src="http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/wordpress-2012.gif" /></p>\r\n<p>We can add one of these beasts, which allow a website owner - with little or no technical knowledge - to edit and update content and photographs.</p>\r\n<p>We work with Wordpress, Joomla, Drupal, and others.</p>\r\n<h3>Search Engine Optimisation</h3>\r\n<p>Have you got a website which is sitting there idle, unknown to the rest of the world?&nbsp;It may be fully functional in all other aspects, but unless it attracts visitors, you may as well not have bothered. We can help in using legitimate methods to drive more search engine traffic to your website.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Code Overhauls</h3>\r\n<p>Your website broken in browser x or y?&nbsp;Loading too slowly?&nbsp;The web is littered with sites coded using out-dated methods. These websites can be stream-lined to load more quickly, display more reliably, and be more easily updated.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Face-lifts</h3>\r\n<p>Do you have a site which looks like it was designed in the previous millenium?&nbsp; Perhaps it was. They say content is king, but visitors are much less likely to explore a web-site which is unattractively designed.</p>\r\n<h3>New Sites&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>We offer a range of services, from simple cookie-cutter brochure-type static web sites to&nbsp; custom-designed fully-functional e-commerce sites.</p>\r\n<p>We also do website code over-hauls, face-lifts, can add content management systems to allow website owners to edit content, and we can speed up your site.</p>\r\n<p>For new sites, we''d like to offer some hard-and-fast quotes, but there are so many variables that that''s almost impossible to do.</p>\r\n<p>Below are some starting points, but you can always <a title="Contact Us" href="/contact/">contact us</a>, tell us what you want, and we''ll send you an obligation-free quote for your new website.</p>\r\n<h3>Content-Management-System -driven sites</h3>\r\n<p>Custom-designed websites including an editable gallery / portfolio /&nbsp; products page, contact page, and the ability to update your site at will !</p>\r\n<h3>From $150</h3>\r\n<p>For businesses, clubs, and individuals wanting to make a first entrance on the web stage:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Brochure-type website</li>\r\n    <li>Bare-bones minimalist but functional design including your logo</li>\r\n    <li>Up to 3 pages including a contact page</li>\r\n    <li>Updates are charged by Urban Legend Web at reasonable rates</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Listed at <a title="Web Design Pros - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://webdesignpros.co.nz/">Web Design Pros</a></p>', 'Services', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'services', '', '', '2012-01-16 23:01:54', '2012-01-16 11:01:54', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/?page_id=90', 0, 'page', '', 0),
