(92, 1, '2009-06-12 00:21:52', '2009-06-11 12:21:52', '<p>Urban Legend web designs, codes, and develops websites.</p>\r\n<h3>Design...</h3>\r\n<p>We''re not from the design school which likes lots of fireworks and whirling things just for the hell of it.</p>\r\n<p>We like sites that are well-designed, yet clean.&nbsp; Simple enough to understand and navigate and enjoy, but not so simple as to suspect the designer is on holiday.</p>\r\n<p>We like to think this site, and most of those in our <a href="/portfolio/" title="View Our Portfolio">portfolio</a>, meet those standards.</p>\r\n<h3>Develop...</h3>\r\n<p>By website development we mean working with, or creating, an engine which drives the site.</p>\r\n<p>For simple websites this may not apply, but even having something as a subscription service may be an advantage.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Home', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-20', '', '', '2009-06-12 00:21:52', '2009-06-11 12:21:52', '', 18, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/06/18-revision-20/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(93, 1, '2009-06-12 00:08:25', '2009-06-11 12:08:25', '<p>Urban Legend web is a sole trader web design and development shop in Whangarei, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>We specialise in building websites for small to medium-sized businesses.</p>\r\n<p>Our focus on&nbsp; <strong>web standards</strong> and best practice coding means that not only will your site load fast, look good, and be easy to update, it will be given its best chance to do well with search engines.</p>\r\n<p>We''re well versed in most of the necessary Acronyms, and know our way around a handful of content management systems, such as&nbsp; <a title="Go to Wordpress'' site" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.com">Wordpress</a>, <a title="Go to osCommerce''s site" target="_blank" href="http://www.oscommerce.com">osCommerce</a>, <a title="Goto Joomla''s site" target="_blank" href="http://www.joomla.org/">Joomla</a>, and proprietary in-house commercial systems.</p>\r\n<p>As well as building websites, we update, and overhaul them.</p>\r\n<p>We work in partnership with Easinet for hosting and other support.</p>\r\n<p><a title="go to our contact page" href="/contact/">Contact us</a> or a&nbsp; quote on your new website.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'About', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-9', '', '', '2009-06-12 00:08:25', '2009-06-11 12:08:25', '', 2, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/06/2-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
