(103, 1, '2009-06-21 02:13:10', '2009-06-20 14:13:10', '<p>We offer a range of services, from a simple brochure-type static web site to a custom-designed fully-functional e-commerce site.</p>\r\n<p>We''d like to offer some hard-and-fast quotes, but there are so many variables that it''s almost impossible to do.</p>\r\n<p>So, below are some starting points:</p>\r\n<h3>From $350</h3>\r\n<p>For s static brochure-type website, with up to 4 pages including a contact page and gallery, and designed from a choice of high-quality templates.</p>\r\n<h3>From $600</h3>\r\n<p>For a brochure-type website as above, but with a custom-made design. Updates are charged by Urban Legend web at a reasonable rate.</p>\r\n<h3>From $900</h3>\r\n<p>For a dynamic website, with a content management system behind it, which allows you, the site owner, to make the updates. With a custom-made design.</p>\r\n<h3>From $1200</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Services', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '90-revision-4', '', '', '2009-06-21 02:13:10', '2009-06-20 14:13:10', '', 90, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/06/90-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(104, 1, '2009-07-05 00:52:23', '2009-07-04 12:52:23', '<p>We offer a range of services, from a simple brochure-type static web site to a custom-designed fully-functional e-commerce site.</p>\r\n<p>Perhaps a list would help?</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>New websites - as we say above, from simple static brochure sites, to fully-blown content management systems, which let you update your site at will</li>\r\n    <li>Updating existing websites. There a number of reasons you might want your website updated :</li>\r\n    <li>As well as all of the above, we''re well-versed in legitimate techniques to get your website noticed by search engines.</li>\r\n    <li>It might need a face-lift, a fresh clean look. </li>\r\n    <li>It might benefit from re-coding to make use of modern technologies for speeding up website delivery, and achieving a consistent look across a website. </li>\r\n    <li>Perhaps you need the ability to interact with your visitors which a database can provide</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>For new sites, we''d like to offer some hard-and-fast quotes, but there are so many variables that that''s almost impossible to do.</p>\r\n<p>Having said that, below are some starting points:</p>\r\n<h3>From $350</h3>\r\n<p>For s static brochure-type website, with up to 4 pages including a contact page and gallery, and designed from a choice of high-quality templates.</p>\r\n<h3>From $600</h3>\r\n<p>For a brochure-type website as above, but with a custom-made design. Updates are charged by Urban Legend web at a reasonable rate.</p>\r\n<h3>From $900</h3>\r\n<p>For a dynamic website, with a content management system behind it, which allows you, the site owner, to make the updates. With a custom-made design.</p>\r\n<h3>From $1200</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Services', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '90-revision-5', '', '', '2009-07-05 00:52:23', '2009-07-04 12:52:23', '', 90, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/07/90-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
