(105, 1, '2009-07-08 00:07:32', '2009-07-07 12:07:32', '<p>We offer a range of services, from simple cookie-cutter brochure-type static web sites to&nbsp; custom-designed fully-functional e-commerce site.</p>\r\n<p>We also offer website coding services, search engine optimisation, website face-lifts, and website code over-hauls.</p>\r\n<p>For new sites, we''d like to offer some hard-and-fast quotes, but there are so many variables that that''s almost impossible to do.</p>\r\n<p>Having said that, below are some starting points:</p>\r\n<h3>From $350</h3>\r\n<p>For a static brochure-type website, with up to 4 pages including a contact page and gallery, and designed from a choice of high-quality templates. </p>\r\n<h3>From $600</h3>\r\n<p>For a brochure-type website as above, but with a custom-made design. Updates are charged by Urban Legend web at a reasonable rate.</p>\r\n<h3>From $900</h3>\r\n<p>For a dynamic website, with a content management system behind it, which allows you, the site owner, to update the site. That includes editing page text, updating image galleries, and more. This option offers a custom-made design.</p>\r\n<h3>From $1200</h3>\r\n<p>More complex sites which may involve forums, and other more complex visitor interaction. Tell us what you need, and we''ll let you know whether we can deliver.</p>\r\n<h3><a name="coding">Website Coding</a></h3>\r\n<p>Urban Legend Web has for some years now worked on a contract basis for McGovern &amp;&nbsp;Associates, a top Auckland web shop, and others. We''re experts at cutting and coding websites using modern methods.</p>\r\n<h3>Search Engine Optimisation</h3>\r\n<p>Have you got a website which is sitting there idle, unknown to the rest of the world?&nbsp;It may be fully functional in all other aspects, but unless it attracts visitors, you may as well not have bothered. We can help in using legitimate methods to drive more search engine traffic to your website.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Code Overhauls</h3>\r\n<p>The web is littered with sites coded using out-dated methods. These websites can be stream-lined to load more quickly, display more reliably, and be more easily updated. </p>\r\n<h3>Website Face-lifts</h3>\r\n<p>Do you have a site which looks like it was designed in the previous millenium?&nbsp; Perhaps it was. They say content is king, but visitors are much less likely to explore a web-site which is unattractively designed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Services', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '90-revision-6', '', '', '2009-07-08 00:07:32', '2009-07-07 12:07:32', '', 90, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/07/90-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(106, 1, '2009-06-13 21:05:14', '2009-06-13 09:05:14', '<p>Urban Legend web is a sole trader web design and development shop in Whangarei, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>We&nbsp; specialise in building websites for small to medium-sized businesses.</p>\r\n<p>Our focus on&nbsp; <strong>web standards</strong> and best practice coding means that not only will your site load fast, look good, and be easy to update, it will be given its best chance to do well with search engines.</p>\r\n<p>We''re well versed in most of the necessary Acronyms, and know our way around a handful of content management systems, such as&nbsp; <a href="http://wordpress.com" target="_blank" title="Go to Wordpress'' site">Wordpress</a>, <a href="http://www.oscommerce.com" target="_blank" title="Go to osCommerce''s site">osCommerce</a>, <a href="http://www.joomla.org/" target="_blank" title="Goto Joomla''s site">Joomla</a>, and proprietary in-house commercial systems.</p>\r\n<p>As well as building websites, we - contractors are used when needed - update, overhaul, and code them for other people. </p>\r\n<p>We work in partnership with Easinet for hosting and other support.</p>\r\n<p><a href="/contact/" title="go to our contact page">Contact us</a> or a&nbsp; quote on your new website.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'About', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-10', '', '', '2009-06-13 21:05:14', '2009-06-13 09:05:14', '', 2, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/06/2-revision-10/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
