(488, 1, '2009-10-04 14:24:44', '2009-10-04 02:24:44', '<p>This site was designed and coded by Urban Legend web, and hosted at <a target="newone" title="easinet - web page hosting made easy" href="http://www.easi.net.nz/web/">Easinet</a>. It re-launched recently using a customised version of the <a title="WeBid - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.webidsupport.com/">WeBid</a> auction engine. This allows the owner to showcase his own stamps, and via a private admin area to manage other users who can also list their stamps.</p>\n<p>It features more than 300 stamps for sale from all over the world, and specialises in African stamps.</p>\n<p>The WeBid engine is coded in PHP&nbsp;and MySQL.</p>', 'Philactica', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '149-revision', '', '', '2009-10-04 14:24:44', '2009-10-04 02:24:44', '', 149, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2009/10/149-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
