(479, 1, '2010-05-25 18:47:21', '2010-05-25 06:47:21', '<p>This site is for a boutique Auckland designer, <a href="http://kalidesigns.co.nz" target="newone" title="Kali Designs\n- opens in new window">Kali Designs</a>, and showcases  the range of original products on offer.</p>\n<p>Products include jewellery boxes, money boxes, wallets, coin purses, bags and glasses case.</p>\n<p>The site allows authorised Kali stockists to log in and order products online, as well as listing product stockists for the general public.</p>', 'Kali Designs', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '327-revision', '', '', '2010-05-25 18:47:21', '2010-05-25 06:47:21', '', 327, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/05/327-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
