(481, 1, '2010-08-04 19:58:47', '2010-08-04 07:58:47', '<p>This service was commissioned by a second-hand book shop, and harvests books information from the internet using a list of book <acronym title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</acronym> numbers.</p>\n<p>Users upload a file containing the ISBN numbers, in either 10- or 13-digit format. On submitting that file, the program reaches out and gathers information - including title, author, publisher, and more - on each book.</p>\n<p>It then writes that information to a file on the web server, and makes that file - in&nbsp; portable-for-databases <acronym title="comma-separated values">csv</acronym> format - available for download.</p>\n<p>The <a href="http://isbn.easi.net.nz" target="newone" title="Urban Legend Book ISBN Harvester - opens in new window">service</a> is password-protected, but a demo is available using the user / password ''demo'' ( for both ).</p>\n<p><a href="/contact">Contact us</a> if you''re a bookseller or small library-owner to discuss using it.</p>', 'ISBN Book harvester', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '434-revision', '', '', '2010-08-04 19:58:47', '2010-08-04 07:58:47', '', 434, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/08/434-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(127, 1, '2009-06-13 20:52:56', '2009-06-13 08:52:56', '<p>Urban Legend web designs, codes, and develops websites.</p>\r\n<h3>Design...</h3>\r\n<p>We''re not from the design school which goes for lots of gizmos and whirling things just because we can.</p>\r\n<p>We like sites that are well-designed, yet clean.&nbsp; Simple enough to understand and navigate and enjoy, but not so simple as to suspect the designer is on holiday.</p>\r\n<p>We like to think this site, and most of those in our <a title="View Our Portfolio" href="/portfolio/">portfolio</a>, meet those standards.</p>\r\n<h3>Develop...</h3>\r\n<p>By website development we mean working with, or creating, an engine which drives the site.</p>\r\n<p>For simple websites this may not apply, but even having something as a subscription service may be an advantage.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Home', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-21', '', '', '2009-06-13 20:52:56', '2009-06-13 08:52:56', '', 18, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/06/18-revision-21/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(128, 1, '2009-09-13 01:36:30', '2009-09-12 13:36:30', '<p>Urban Legend web is based in Whangarei, Northland, New Zealand, and designs, codes, and develops websites.</p>\n<h3>Design...</h3>\n<p>We''re not from the design school which goes for lots of gizmos and whirling things just because we can.</p>\n<p>We like sites that are well-designed, yet clean.&nbsp; Simple enough to understand and navigate and enjoy, but not so simple as to suspect the designer is on holiday.</p>\n<p>We like to think this site, and most of those in our <a href="/portfolio/" title="View Our Portfolio">portfolio</a>, meet those standards.</p>\n<h3>Develop...</h3>\n<p>By website development we mean working with, or creating, an ''engine'' which drives dynamic website. These are commonly known as Content Management Systems, and can allow website owners to edit website content, use databases, create a gallery of images, run a subscription service, and more.</p>\n<h3>Simpler Websites...</h3>\n<p>Or, you may need a simple brochure-type site, which&nbsp; is used to showcase projects or products, and&nbsp; as a contact point for new and current customers. We do these too, so please feel free to <a href="/contact/">contact us</a> for a free, no-obligation quote.</p>\n<p><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Home', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-autosave', '', '', '2009-09-13 01:36:30', '2009-09-12 13:36:30', '', 18, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/09/18-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
