u want your site to achieve a financial target, are you focussed on attracting new customers, or do you have a readership target you want to meet?&nbsp; </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Home', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-25', '', '', '2009-09-15 18:37:47', '2009-09-15 06:37:47', '', 18, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/09/18-revision-25/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
