(135, 1, '2009-07-08 00:27:57', '2009-07-07 12:27:57', '<p>Urban Legend web is a sole trader web design and development shop in Whangarei, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>We specialise in building websites for small to medium-sized businesses, and in contract website coding.</p>\r\n<p>Our focus on&nbsp; <strong>web standards</strong> and best practice coding means that not only will your site load fast, look good, and be easy to update, it will be given its best chance to do well with search engines.</p>\r\n<p>We''re well versed in most of the necessary Acronyms, and know our way around a handful of content management systems, such as&nbsp; <a title="Go to Wordpress'' site" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.com">Wordpress</a>, <a title="Go to osCommerce''s site" target="_blank" href="http://www.oscommerce.com">osCommerce</a>, <a title="Goto Joomla''s site" target="_blank" href="http://www.joomla.org/">Joomla</a>, and proprietary in-house commercial systems.</p>\r\n<p>As well as building websites, we update, overhaul, and code them for other people.</p>\r\n<p>We work in partnership with Easinet for hosting and other support.</p>\r\n<p><a title="go to our contact page" href="/contact/">Contact us</a> or a&nbsp; quote on your new website.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'About', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-11', '', '', '2009-07-08 00:27:57', '2009-07-07 12:27:57', '', 2, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/07/2-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(136, 1, '2009-09-15 22:06:37', '2009-09-15 10:06:37', '<p>Urban Legend web is a sole trader web design and development shop, run by Duncan O''Neill,&nbsp; in Whangarei, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>We - including hired hands when necessary -&nbsp; specialise in building websites for small to medium-sized businesses, and in contract website coding.</p>\r\n<p>Our focus on&nbsp; <strong>web standards</strong> and best practice coding means that not only will your site load fast, look good, and be easy to update, it will be given its best chance to do well with search engines.</p>\r\n<p>We''re well versed in most of the necessary Acronyms, and know our way around a handful of content management systems, such as&nbsp; <a href="http://wordpress.com" target="_blank" title="Go to Wordpress'' site">Wordpress</a>, <a href="http://www.oscommerce.com" target="_blank" title="Go to osCommerce''s site">osCommerce</a>, <a href="http://www.joomla.org/" target="_blank" title="Goto Joomla''s site">Joomla</a>, and proprietary in-house commercial systems.</p>\r\n<p>As well as building websites, we update, overhaul, and code them for other people.</p>\r\n<p>We work in partnership with <a href="http://www.easi.net.nz" target="newone" title="visit Easinet''s site - opens in new window">Easinet</a> for hosting and other support.</p>\r\n<p><a href="/contact/" title="go to our contact page">Contact us</a> for a&nbsp; quote.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'About', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-12', '', '', '2009-09-15 22:06:37', '2009-09-15 10:06:37', '', 2, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/2009/09/2-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
