(537, 1, '2010-09-06 22:53:12', '2010-09-06 10:53:12', '<p>I''ve been snuffling around in my archives, dusting off long-forgotten back-up CDs and such, and found an interesting&nbsp; <a title="Palette Picker" href="/colorpicker/">wee toy</a> I''d almost forgotten writing.</p>\r\n<p>It''s a basic <a href="/colorpicker/">palette picker</a>, written as a web-page, which allows the user to choose a web-page colour scheme from the <a title="Visibone''s 216-colour chart - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.visibone.com/colorlab/">216 basic colours</a>.</p>\r\n<p>There are four colour-able areas. You fill them by clicking a colour from the panel on the left, and then in one of the colour-able areas. A cookie will save the scheme you decided on, and CSS codes for the color are given.</p>\r\n<p>I&nbsp;did say it''s basic :&nbsp;I wrote it in <strong>2002</strong>, using Javascript,&nbsp; before the days of JQuery. The code is embedded rather than linked, so it''s easy to see (&nbsp;and modify if you choose ).</p>\r\n<p>Who knows, it may be useful, but probably more likely a 5-minute diversion. <a href="colorpicker/" title="try out the palette picker">Have at it</a>!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'The Palette Picker', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '533-revision-3', '', '', '2010-09-06 22:53:12', '2010-09-06 10:53:12', '', 533, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/09/533-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(159, 1, '2010-01-23 12:53:53', '2010-01-23 00:53:53', '<p>We offer a range of services, from simple cookie-cutter brochure-type static web sites to&nbsp; custom-designed fully-functional e-commerce sites.</p>\r\n<p>We also offer website coding services, search engine optimisation, website face-lifts, and website code over-hauls.</p>\r\n<p>For new sites, we''d like to offer some hard-and-fast quotes, but there are so many variables that that''s almost impossible to do.</p>\r\n<p>Below are some starting points, but you can always <a title="Contact Us" href="/contact/">contact us</a>, tell us what you want, and we''ll send you an obligation-free quote for your new website.</p>\r\n<h3>From $300</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Brochure-type website</li>\r\n    <li>Designed from a choice of high-quality templates</li>\r\n    <li>Up to 4 pages including a contact page and gallery</li>\r\n    <li>Basic search-engine submission</li>\r\n    <li>Updates are charged by Urban Legend Web at a reasonable rate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>From $500</h3>\r\n<p>All of the above, but with an <strong>original, custom design</strong>, and up to 5 pages.</p>\r\n<h3>From $900</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Dynamic website</li>\r\n    <li>Using a <strong>content management system</strong> which allows you, the site owner, to update the site. That includes editing page text, updating image galleries, and more.</li>\r\n    <li>Original, custom design</li>\r\n    <li>Unlimited pages</li>\r\n    <li>Email subscription service</li>\r\n    <li>Search engine optimisation</li>\r\n    <li>Other add-ons as negotiated</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>From $1200</h3>\r\n<p>All of the above but with other more complex options, which may involve forums, secure areas of the website, or other customisations. Any and all extras you can think of. <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a> to find out more.</p>\r\n<h3><a name="coding">Website Coding</a></h3>\r\n<p>Urban Legend Web has for some years now worked on a contract basis for <a href="http://www.mcgovern.co.nz">McGovern &amp;&nbsp;Associates</a>, a top Auckland web shop, and others. We''re experts at cutting and coding websites using modern methods.</p>\r\n<h3>Search Engine Optimisation</h3>\r\n<p>Have you got a website which is sitting there idle, unknown to the rest of the world?&nbsp;It may be fully functional in all other aspects, but unless it attracts visitors, you may as well not have bothered. We can help in using legitimate methods to drive more search engine traffic to your website.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Code Overhauls</h3>\r\n<p>The web is littered with sites coded using out-dated methods. These websites can be stream-lined to load more quickly, display more reliably, and be more easily updated.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Face-lifts</h3>\r\n<p>Do you have a site which looks like it was designed in the previous millenium?&nbsp; Perhaps it was. They say content is king, but visitors are much less likely to explore a web-site which is unattractively designed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Services', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '90-revision-8', '', '', '2010-01-23 12:53:53', '2010-01-23 00:53:53', '', 90, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/01/90-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
