(527, 1, '2010-05-28 14:16:40', '2010-05-28 02:16:40', '<p>Urban Legend web is based in Whangarei, Northland, New Zealand, and designs, codes, updates, and develops websites.</p>\r\n<h3>Web Development...</h3>\r\n<p><img width="138" height="96" src="http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/cogs21.gif" alt="cogs" title="cogs" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-391" />By website development we mean working with, or creating, an ''engine'' which drives dynamic websites. The pre-packaged versions of these are commonly known as Content Management Systems, and can allow website owners to edit content, list and sell products, create an image gallery, run a subscription service, and more. We also produce our own simple purpose-built ''engines''.</p>\r\n<h3>Web Design...</h3>\r\n<p><img width="138" height="96" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-400" title="draughting table" alt="draughting table" src="http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/table4.gif" />We''re not from the design school which packs in gizmos and whirling things just because we can.</p>\r\n<p>We prefer to see and build web sites that are well-designed, yet clean, and fast-loading.&nbsp; In other words, sites which are built for end users - simple enough to understand, navigate and enjoy, but designed well enough for those users to enjoy. We like to think this site, and most of those in our <a title="View Our Portfolio" href="/portfolio/">portfolio</a>, meet those standards.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Simpler Websites...</h3>\r\n<p>If on the other hand you need a simple brochure-type site, which doesn''t change often, and is used mostly as a contact point for customers, club members, friends, or readers, we do these too.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Hire us because...</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>We''re <strong>affordable</strong>. Many small-to-medium sized businesses, or clubs, don''t have bottomless pockets. We''ll give you a quote, not a fright, and stick to that figure.</li>\r\n    <li>We build <strong>web sites</strong> which <strong>load fast</strong>, and display reliably across a range of platforms and operating systems, thanks to the use of modern methods of coding to <def title="eXtensible Mark-up Language">XHTML</def> and <def title="Cascading Style Sheets">CSS standards</def>.</li>\r\n    <li>We build sites which <strong>look good.</strong></li>\r\n    <li>Your site will be <strong>noticed</strong>. Our coding methods, and search engine knowledge give your website the best chance of being prominent in the relevant search engine results.&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>We focus on what''s important to you. For example, do you want your site to achieve a financial target, are you focussed on attracting new customers, or do you have a readership target you want to meet?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>To get started,&nbsp; <a title="go to our contact page" href="/contact/">contact us</a> now for a free, no-obligation quote for your website work.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Home', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-39', '', '', '2010-05-28 14:16:40', '2010-05-28 02:16:40', '', 18, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/05/18-revision-39/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
