(512, 1, '2009-10-04 13:49:10', '2009-10-04 01:49:10', '<p>This site is for a top Auckland photographer who was the official photographer for the Dalai Lama of Tibet on his last visit to these shores.</p>\n<p>Its design, by Urban Legend web, is intended to take a back seat to the photgraphs, many of which are stunning. It features a gallery of images sorted by subject, with a custom-built engine written in PHP.</p>\n<p>As is standard practice at Urban Legend web, It is coded to <a title="visit The Web Standards Project - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.webstandards.org/">web standards</a> using valid XHTML and CSS</p>', 'Jacqui Walker, Photographer', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '145-revision', '', '', '2009-10-04 13:49:10', '2009-10-04 01:49:10', '', 145, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2009/10/145-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
