(149, 1, '2009-10-04 14:24:44', '2009-10-04 02:24:44', '<p>This site was designed and coded by Urban Legend web, and hosted at</p>\r\n<p><a title="easinet - web page hosting made easy" target="newone" href="http://www.easi.net.nz/web/">Easinet</a></p>\r\n<p>. It re-launched recently using a customised version of the</p>\r\n<p><a target="newone" title="WeBid - opens in new window" href="http://www.webidsupport.com/">WeBid</a></p>\r\n<p>auction engine. This allows the owner to showcase his own stamps, and via a private admin area to manage other users who can also list their stamps.</p>\r\n<p>It features more than 300 stamps for sale from all over the world, and specialises in African stamps.</p>\r\n<p>The WeBid engine is coded in PHP&nbsp;and MySQL.</p>', 'Philactica', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'philactica', '', '', '2012-01-21 14:02:23', '2012-01-21 02:02:23', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/?p=149', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(156, 1, '2009-10-04 15:56:32', '2009-10-04 03:56:32', '<p>This site was is for the birthplace of one of New Zealand''s most famous authors, Katherine Mansfield. It is designed by Helen Smith of <a title="McGovern &amp; Associates - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.mcgovern.co.nz/">McGovern &amp; Associates</a>, and hand-coded from supplied files. It is an early example&nbsp; of the use of the use of <dfn title="Cascading Style Sheets">CSS</dfn> for layout. The site is driven by an in-house content management system.</p>', 'Katherine Mansfield House', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'katherine-mansfield-house', '', '', '2012-01-16 22:40:29', '2012-01-16 10:40:29', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegend.co.nz/?p=156', 0, 'post', '', 0),
