(498, 1, '2009-10-04 13:28:41', '2009-10-04 01:28:41', '<p>This site is for an Auckland art gallery, and is designed by Helen Smith of <a target="newone" title="McGovern &amp; Associates - opens in new window" href="http://www.mcgovern.co.nz/">McGovern &amp; Associates</a>. Its layout, including top-level subsections, is coded by Urban Legend web. It uses McGovern''s content management system to allow the client to enter and edit content.</p>', 'John Leech Gallery', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '142-revision', '', '', '2009-10-04 13:28:41', '2009-10-04 01:28:41', '', 142, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2009/10/142-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(238, 1, '2010-02-24 00:11:10', '2010-02-24 00:11:10', '<p>This is an e-commerce enabled website for a Whangarei bookseller specialising in rare, collectible, and historical New Zealand books.</p>\r\n<p>It is designed by Urban Legend web, and uses the Wordpress engine, along with a heavily adapted version of the WP <a title="WP e-Commerce plugin - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.instinct.co.nz/e-commerce/">e-Commerce plugin</a>.</p>\r\n<p>As is standard with Urban Legend web sites, this site is designed using valid XHTML, and CSS for layout.</p>', 'Market Books', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'market-books-2', '', '', '2011-04-13 22:56:10', '2011-04-13 10:56:10', '', 0, 'http://ul.xp-home/?p=238', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(167, 1, '2010-02-26 02:27:44', '2010-02-26 02:27:44', '<p>The site owners contracted Urban Legend web to update the Wordpress engine, make changes and additions to the site template, add functionality and advertising, and migrate the standards-based site to a new host.</p>', '71 miles', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '71-miles', '', '', '2012-01-21 13:58:19', '2012-01-21 01:58:19', '', 0, 'http://ul.xp-home/?p=167', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(194, 1, '2010-02-26 09:05:24', '2010-02-26 09:05:24', '<p>This <a title="Le Petit Hotel parent site - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.lepetithotel.co.nz/">site</a> was recently integrated with the <a title="Wordrpress.org - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://wordpress.org">Wordpress</a> engine, and is designed by Urban Legend design in collaboration with the owner.</p>\r\n<p>It features a custom contact form, and uses widgets and other Wordpress functionality to control the left-bar content. It is hosted at <a title="Easinet - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.easi.net.nz">Easinet</a></p>', 'Le Petit Hotel', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'le-petit-hotel-2', '', '', '2012-01-21 14:00:34', '2012-01-21 02:00:34', '', 0, 'http://ul.xp-home/?p=194', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(249, 1, '2010-02-27 03:01:53', '2010-02-27 03:01:53', '<p>This site is for an Auckland law-firm specialising in corporate and commercial law.</p>\r\n<p>Urban Legend web was contracted by McGovern &amp;&nbsp;Associates to convert the site to valid (X)HTML&nbsp;and CSS, and integrate it with McGovern''s in-house ASP.NET-based &quot;Scripts&quot; Content Management System.</p>', 'Mclean Law', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'mclean-law', '', '', '2012-01-16 22:42:17', '2012-01-16 10:42:17', '', 0, 'http://ul.xp-home/?p=249', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(275, 1, '2010-05-16 00:19:19', '2010-05-16 00:19:19', '<p>This site is for a Whangarei ISP which contracts Urban Legend web to provide website development and design.</p>\r\n<p>The aim was for an effective, fast-loading, and simple design, as befitted the state of browsers at the time, and an emphasis on content.</p>\r\n<p>It uses a flash animation on the landing page, and contains copies of newspaper articles for new computer users.</p>', 'Easinet', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'easinet', '', '', '2012-01-16 22:46:24', '2012-01-16 10:46:24', '', 0, 'http://ul.xp-home/?p=275', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(235, 1, '2010-02-26 23:40:13', '2010-02-26 23:40:13', '<p><img width="185" height="116" src="http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/MB.gif" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>This e-commerce enabled website allows a bookshop to showcase their catalogue online.</p>\r\n<p>Market Books specialises in New Zealand subjects, as well as a stocking a wide range of hard-to-find non-fiction titles.</p>\r\n<p>The website uses the <a href="http://wordpress.org">Wordpress</a> engine with the <a href="http://www.instinct.co.nz/e-commerce/">WP E-commerce plugin</a> to allow the shop to present their catalogue.</p>', 'Market Books', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '98-revision-10', '', '', '2010-02-26 23:40:13', '2010-02-26 23:40:13', '', 98, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/02/98-revision-10/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
