(441, 1, '2010-05-28 12:43:31', '2010-05-28 00:43:31', '<h3><a name="coding">Website Coding</a></h3>\r\n<p>Urban Legend Web has for some years now worked on a contract basis for <a href="http://www.mcgovern.co.nz">McGovern &amp;&nbsp;Associates</a>, a top Auckland web shop, and others. We''re experts at cutting and coding websites using modern methods.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Content Management Systems</h3>\r\n<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-414" alt="wordpress" title="wordpress" width="138" height="96" src="http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/wordpress2.gif" />We can add one of these beasts, which allow a website owner - with little or no technical knowledge - to edit and update content and photographs.</p>\r\n<p>We work with Wordpress, Joomla, Drupal, and others.</p>\r\n<h3>Search Engine Optimisation</h3>\r\n<p>Have you got a website which is sitting there idle, unknown to the rest of the world?&nbsp;It may be fully functional in all other aspects, but unless it attracts visitors, you may as well not have bothered. We can help in using legitimate methods to drive more search engine traffic to your website.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Code Overhauls</h3>\r\n<p>Your website broken in browser x or y?&nbsp;Loading too slowly?&nbsp;The web is littered with sites coded using out-dated methods. These websites can be stream-lined to load more quickly, display more reliably, and be more easily updated.</p>\r\n<h3>Website Face-lifts</h3>\r\n<p>Do you have a site which looks like it was designed in the previous millenium?&nbsp; Perhaps it was. They say content is king, but visitors are much less likely to explore a web-site which is unattractively designed.</p>\r\n<h3>New Sites&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>We offer a range of services, from simple cookie-cutter brochure-type static web sites to&nbsp; custom-designed fully-functional e-commerce sites.</p>\r\n<p>We also do website code over-hauls, face-lifts, can add content management systems to allow website owners to edit content, and we can speed up your site.</p>\r\n<p>For new sites, we''d like to offer some hard-and-fast quotes, but there are so many variables that that''s almost impossible to do.</p>\r\n<p>Below are some starting points, but you can always <a title="Contact Us" href="/contact/">contact us</a>, tell us what you want, and we''ll send you an obligation-free quote for your new website.</p>\r\n<h3>From $150</h3>\r\n<p>For businesses, clubs, and individuals wanting to make a first entrance on the web stage:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Brochure-type website</li>\r\n    <li>Bare-bones minimalist but functional design including your logo</li>\r\n    <li>Up to 3 pages including a contact page</li>\r\n    <li>Updates are charged by Urban Legend Web at reasonable rates</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>From $600</h3>\r\n<p>All of the above, but with an <strong>original, custom design</strong>, and up to 5 pages, including a gallery page.</p>\r\n<h3>From $800</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Dynamic website</li>\r\n    <li>Using a <strong>content management system</strong> which allows you, the site owner, to update the site. That includes editing page text, updating image galleries, and more.</li>\r\n    <li>Original, custom design</li>\r\n    <li>Unlimited pages</li>\r\n    <li>Email subscription service</li>\r\n    <li>Search engine optimisation</li>\r\n    <li>Other add-ons as negotiated</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<a name="coding"><br />\r\n</a></p>\r\n<h3><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Services', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '90-revision-24', '', '', '2010-05-28 12:43:31', '2010-05-28 00:43:31', '', 90, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/05/90-revision-24/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(443, 1, '2010-08-29 01:51:54', '2010-08-28 13:51:54', '<p>I''ve spent some time recently exploring the new features in Wordpress 3.0.1, and learning about very useful <a href="http://themeshaper.com/wordpress-child-theme-basics/" target="newone" title="from Thematic how to modify themes the smart way - opens in new window">child themes</a> and theme frameworks.</p>\r\n<p>For now the only visible improvements on this site are to do with the search function. Target words are now <span class="hilite">highlighted</span> in search results, both from within and outside this website.</p>\r\n<p>More improvements, and some original themes, to come....</p>', 'Wordpress 301', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress-301', '', '', '2010-08-29 02:15:11', '2010-08-28 14:15:11', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/?p=443', 0, 'post', '', 0),
