(587, 1, '2010-05-27 15:34:56', '2010-05-27 03:34:56', '<p>Urban Legend web is a sole trader web design and development shop, run by Duncan O''Neill,&nbsp; in Whangarei, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>We - including hired help when necessary -&nbsp; specialise in contract website coding, updating and improving existing websites, and building websites for small to medium-sized businesses.</p>\r\n<p><img width="100" height="157" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-404" title="Duncan O''Neill" alt="Duncan O''Neill" src="http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/me1.jpg" />Our focus on&nbsp; <strong>web standards</strong> and best practice coding means that not only will your site load fast, look good, and be easy to update, it will be given its best chance to do well with search engines.</p>\r\n<p>We''re well versed in most of the necessary Acronyms, and know our way around a handful of content management systems, such as&nbsp; <a title="Go to Wordpress'' site" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.com">Wordpress</a>, <a title="Go to osCommerce''s site" target="_blank" href="http://www.oscommerce.com">osCommerce</a>, <a title="Goto Joomla''s site" target="_blank" href="http://www.joomla.org/">Joomla</a>, and proprietary in-house commercial systems.</p>\r\n<p>As well as building websites, we update, overhaul, and code them for other people.</p>\r\n<p>We work in partnership with <a title="visit Easinet''s site - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.easi.net.nz">Easinet</a> for hosting and other support.</p>\r\n<p><a title="go to our contact page" href="/contact/">Contact us</a> for a&nbsp; quote.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'About', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-18', '', '', '2010-05-27 15:34:56', '2010-05-27 03:34:56', '', 2, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/05/2-revision-18/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(604, 1, '2011-04-20 21:00:33', '2011-04-20 09:00:33', '<p>Some recent contract work just completed, via <a href="http://immersionmedia.com/" target="newone" title="visit Immersion Media - opens in new window">Immersion Media</a>, a California company;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><a href="http://valueinvestingcongress.com/" target="newone" title="visit Value Investing Congress - opens in new window">Value Investing Congress</a> ; I updated the jQuery behind the front-page slider to increase the delay for some slides</li>\r\n    <li><a href="http://valueinvestingletter.com" target="newone" title="visite Value Investing Letter - opens in new window">Value Investing Letter</a>; I updated the <a title="opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://valueinvestingletter.com/value-investing-letter-video.html">video landing page</a> by editing some <acronym title="php.net">PHP</acronym> files behind the <a title="the modx content management system - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://modx.com/">modx</a> content management system which drives the site, and some <acronym title="cascading Style Sheets">CSS</acronym> files for styling.</li>\r\n    <li>On the same site, we wrote code to protect privileged <a title="opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://valueinvestingletter.com/pdfs/Why_We_Covered_Our_Netflix_Short_T2%20Partners-2-9-11.pdf">pdf files</a> from unregistered viewers</li>\r\n    <li>And lastly, I updated code to ensure financial data stability on <a title="visit fgiworldwatch.com - opens in new window" target="new" href="http://fgiworldwatch.com">this site </a>and on <a title="fgiworldwatch.com financial data - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://fgiworldwatchreport.com/market-data.html">this page</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Recent Work', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'recent-work', '', '', '2011-06-27 12:46:27', '2011-06-27 00:46:27', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/?p=604', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(590, 1, '2011-04-13 20:32:38', '2011-04-13 08:32:38', '<p>This <a title="visit elisacachero.com - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://elisacachero.com">portfolio site</a> is for multi-disciplinary designer Elisa Cachero, and shows her design work in textiles, art direction, print &amp;&nbsp;web design, and event planning.</p>\r\n<p>It uses the Wordpress engine with the popular portfolio theme <a title="autofocus pro demo - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://fthrwght.com/autofocus/plusdemo/">Autofocuspro</a> . Urban Legend web was contracted via <a title="visit wpqestions.com - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://wpquestions.com">wpquestions.com</a> to update that theme so that;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>the front page displays in the way usually used for category pages</li>\r\n    <li>the number of posts shown beneath the feature image on the home page is limited</li>\r\n    <li>copyright information can be included on single post <a title="example of a single post page using a slider with copyright information" target="newone" href="http://www.elisacachero.com/282/textile_product/product/marie-clutch/">pages</a> which use the JQuery image slider</li>\r\n    <li>the default ''next'' and ''previous'' post arrows on the front page are hidden</li>\r\n    <li>show front-page post titles only on mouse hover</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Via the wpqestions.com site, I''ve now worked on a number of Wordpress autofocuspro installations, and invite <a title="Contact Us" href="http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/contact/">further queries</a> relating to that theme.</p>', 'ElisaCachero.com', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'elisacachero-com', '', '', '2012-01-21 14:01:21', '2012-01-21 02:01:21', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/?p=590', 0, 'post', '', 0),
