(595, 1, '2010-08-31 23:58:51', '2010-08-31 11:58:51', '<p>This is an e-commerce enabled website for a Whangarei bookseller specialising in rare, collectible, and historical New Zealand books.</p>\r\n<p>It is designed by Urban Legend web, and uses the Wordpress engine, along with a heavily adapted version of the WP <a href="http://www.instinct.co.nz/e-commerce/" target="newone" title="WP e-Commerce plugin - opens in new window">e-Commerce plugin</a>.</p>\r\n<p>As is standard with Urban Legend web sites, this site is designed using valid XHTML, and CSS for layout.</p>', 'Market Books', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '238-revision-2', '', '', '2010-08-31 23:58:51', '2010-08-31 11:58:51', '', 238, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/08/238-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
