(602, 1, '2010-09-01 11:36:55', '2010-08-31 23:36:55', '<p>This site is for a boutique Auckland designer, <a title="Kali Designs - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://kalidesigns.co.nz">Kali Designs</a>, and showcases  the range of original products on offer.</p>\r\n<p>Products include jewellery boxes, money boxes, wallets, coin purses, bags and glasses case.</p>\r\n<p>The site allows authorised Kali stockists to log in and order products online, as well as listing product stockists for the general public.</p>', 'Kali Designs', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '327-revision-3', '', '', '2010-09-01 11:36:55', '2010-08-31 23:36:55', '', 327, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/09/327-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(603, 1, '2010-10-19 14:33:57', '2010-10-19 02:33:57', '<p>This site, <a href="http://thedesignerslibrary.co.nz" target="newone" title="The Designers Library - opens in new window"> The Designers Library</a>, is for a soft-furnishings (&nbsp;curtains , blinds etc ) company in Hamilton, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>It is designed by <a href="http://www.box.co.nz/" target="newone" title="CubeMedia - opens in new window">CubeMedia</a>, and converted into a fully-functional Wordpress - powered website by Urban Legend Web.</p>\r\n<p>It uses a JQuery - based slider for the slideshow on the front page, and a semi-transparent background for the centered content area. A&nbsp;combination of native Wordpress abilities, plugins, and customised templates drive the site.</p>', 'The Designers Library', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '538-revision-17', '', '', '2010-10-19 14:33:57', '2010-10-19 02:33:57', '', 538, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/10/538-revision-17/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
