(858, 1, '2011-11-21 11:10:03', '2011-11-20 23:10:03', '<p>This site is for a NZ-government agency, <acronym title="Forestry Emissions Trust Unit">FEUT</acronym>, which manages carbon emissions for government-owned forests.</p>\r\n<p>The site design is by <a title="visit McGovern.co.nz - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://mcgovern.co.nz/">McGovern &amp; Associates</a>, and coded into a custom WordPress theme by Urban Legend web.</p>\r\n<p>The site is coded in HTML5, and features some custom jQuery in the <a title="visit the licensed crown forests section of the site" target="newone" href="http://feut.org.nz/licensed-crown-forests/">Licensed Crown Forests</a> section, and on the <a target="newone" title="visit the contact page - opens in new window" href="http://feut.org.nz/contact/">contact page</a>. It also gives its owners the ability to update a forests database from an uploaded Excel file using a customised WordPress plugin.</p>\r\n<p>It uses modern <a target="newone" title="font-face news from A LIst Apart" href="http://www.alistapart.com/articles/fonts-at-the-crossing/">@Font-face coding</a> to render the desired font family across platforms.</p>', 'FEUT', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'feut', '', '', '2012-01-21 12:55:22', '2012-01-21 00:55:22', '', 0, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/?p=858', 0, 'post', '', 0),
