(865, 1, '2012-01-21 11:10:03', '2012-01-20 23:10:03', '<p>This site is for a NZ-government agency, <acronym title="Forestry Emissions Trust Unit">FEUT</acronym>, which manages carbon emissions for government-owned forests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The site design is by <a href="http://mcgovern.co.nz/" title="visit McGovern.co.nz - opens in new window" target="newone">McGovern &amp; Associates</a>, and coded into a custom WordPress theme by Urban Legend web.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The site is coded in HTML5, and features some custom jQuery in the <a href="http://feut.org.nz/licensed-crown-forests/" title="visit the licensed crown forests section of the site" target="newone">Licensed Crown Forests</a> section, and on the <a href="http://feut.org.nz/contact/" target="newone" title="visit the contact page - opens in new window">contact page</a>. It also gives its owners the ability to update a forests database from an uploaded Excel file using a customised WordPress plugin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It uses modern <a href="http://www.alistapart.com/articles/fonts-at-the-crossing/" target="newone" title="font-face news from A LIst Apart">@Font-face coding</a> to render the desired font family across platforms.</p> ', 'FEUT', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '858-revision-2', '', '', '2012-01-21 11:10:03', '2012-01-20 23:10:03', '', 858, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/858-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
