(872, 1, '2012-01-16 13:04:20', '2012-01-16 01:04:20', '<p>This site is <a title="visit te-awa.org.nz - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://te-awa.org.nz">te-awa.org.nz</a>, The Great New Zealand River Ride, an outdoors project based on New Zealand''s largest rvier, the&nbsp; Waikato.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUrban Legend web was contracted by<a title="visit Cube Media - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://box.co.nz"> Cube Media</a> to install and configure <a title="visit Wordpress.org - opens in new window" href="http://wordpress.org">wordpress</a>, code an original theme using that publishing platform, and based on supplied graphics, and add functional extensions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe site features a JQuery slider on the front page, a JQuery-based drop-down menu, custom widgets, and customised plugins, including a subscription service.</p>', 'Te Awa | The Great New Zealand River Ride', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '572-revision-15', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:04:20', '2012-01-16 01:04:20', '', 572, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/572-revision-15/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(873, 1, '2012-01-16 13:06:29', '2012-01-16 01:06:29', '<p>The site owners contracted Urban Legend web to update the Wordpress engine, make changes and additions to the site template, add functionality and advertising, and migrate the standards-based site to a new host.</p>', '71 miles', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '167-revision-5', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:06:29', '2012-01-16 01:06:29', '', 167, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/167-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(874, 1, '2011-06-07 19:50:29', '2011-06-07 07:50:29', '<p>This site carries financial news, including <a href="http://fgiworldwatchreport.com/market-data.html" target="newone" title="visit FGI WorldWatch - opens in new window">market data</a>, from the US, and around the world.</p>\r\n<p>Urban Legend web was contracted to update server-side <dfn title="Hypertext Preprocessor - http://php.net">PHP</dfn> code, and the timing of automatic feeds, to ensure data stability.</p>\r\n<p>We also made some small presentational changes to the table data.</p>', 'FGI Worldwatch', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '612-revision-12', '', '', '2011-06-07 19:50:29', '2011-06-07 07:50:29', '', 612, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2011/06/612-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(875, 1, '2012-01-16 13:10:44', '2012-01-16 01:10:44', '<p>This site is for a boutique Auckland designer, <a target="newone" title="Kali Designs - opens in new window" href="http://kalidesigns.co.nz">Kali Designs</a>, and showcases  the range of original products on offer.</p>\r\n<p>It is designed by Urban Legend web and the owner.</p>\r\n<p>Products include jewellery boxes, money boxes, wallets, coin purses, bags and glasses case.</p>\r\n<p>The site allows authorised Kali stockists to log in and order products online, as well as listing product stockists for the general public.</p>', 'Kali Designs', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '327-revision-5', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:10:44', '2012-01-16 01:10:44', '', 327, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/327-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(876, 1, '2012-01-16 13:15:36', '2012-01-16 01:15:36', '<p>The T&Aring;&laquo;hoe Establishment Trust was set up to manage funds and assets transferred to the T&Aring;&laquo;hoe tribe as part of its Waitangi Tribunal settlement with the New Zealand government.</p>\r\n<p>This website was launched in 2010, and designed by McGovern &amp;&nbsp;Associates. They in turn contracted Urban Legend web to cut and code the site templates from supplied photoshop files.</p>', 'Tuhoe Establishment Trust', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '356-revision-3', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:15:36', '2012-01-16 01:15:36', '', 356, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/356-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(877, 1, '2012-01-16 13:09:12', '2012-01-16 01:09:12', '<p>Urban Legend web was contracted by <a target="newone" title="visit McGovern &amp; Associates - opens in new window" href="www.mcgovern.co.nz">McGovern &amp; Associates</a> to hand-code the templates for this website, for the Auckland Writers and Readers Festival 2010.</p>\r\n<p>The site uses the <a title="about cufon" target="newone" href="http://wiki.github.com/sorccu/cufon/about">cufon</a> technology to render text headings as images, and is coded in valid XHTML and CSS.</p>\r\n<p>It is backed by McGovern''s proprietary <acronym title="Content Management System">CMS</acronym> allowing its owners to edit content.</p>', 'Auckland Writers and Readers Festival', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '283-revision-6', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:09:12', '2012-01-16 01:09:12', '', 283, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/283-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(878, 1, '2011-04-13 23:11:37', '2011-04-13 11:11:37', '<p>This site, <a title="The Designers Library - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://thedesignerslibrary.co.nz"> The Designers Library</a>, is for a soft-furnishings (&nbsp;curtains , blinds etc ) company in Hamilton, New Zealand.</p>\r\n<p>It is designed by <a title="CubeMedia - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.box.co.nz/">CubeMedia</a>, and converted into a fully-functional Wordpress - powered website by Urban Legend Web.</p>\r\n<p>It uses a JQuery - based slider for the slideshow on the front page, and a semi-transparent background for the centered content area. A&nbsp;combination of native Wordpress abilities, plugins, and customised templates drive the site.</p>', 'The Designers Library', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '538-revision-18', '', '', '2011-04-13 23:11:37', '2011-04-13 11:11:37', '', 538, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2011/04/538-revision-18/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(879, 1, '2012-01-16 13:14:17', '2012-01-16 01:14:17', '<p>This <a title="Le Petit Hotel parent site - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.lepetithotel.co.nz/">site</a> was recently integrated with the <a title="Wordrpress.org - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://wordpress.org">Wordpress</a> engine, and is designed by Urban Legend design in collaboration with the owner.</p>\r\n<p>It features a custom contact form, and uses widgets and other Wordpress functionality to control the left-bar content. It is hosted at <a title="Easinet - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://www.easi.net.nz">Easinet</a></p>', 'Le Petit Hotel', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '194-revision-4', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:14:17', '2012-01-16 01:14:17', '', 194, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/194-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(880, 1, '2012-01-16 13:13:05', '2012-01-16 01:13:05', '<p>This service was commissioned by a second-hand book shop, and harvests books information from the internet using a list of book <acronym title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</acronym> numbers.</p>\r\n<p>Users upload a file containing the ISBN numbers, in either 10- or 13-digit format. On submitting that file, the program reaches out and gathers information - including title, author, publisher, and more - on each book.</p>\r\n<p>It then writes that information to a file on the web server, and makes that file - in&nbsp; portable-for-databases <acronym title="comma-separated values">csv</acronym> format - available for download.</p>\r\n<p>The <a target="newone" title="Urban Legend Book ISBN Harvester - opens in new window" href="http://isbn.easi.net.nz">service</a> is password-protected, but a demo is available using the user / password ''demo'' ( for both ).</p>\r\n<p><a href="/contact">Contact us</a> if you''re a bookseller or small library-owner to discuss using it.</p>', 'ISBN Book harvester', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '434-revision-4', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:13:05', '2012-01-16 01:13:05', '', 434, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/434-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(881, 1, '2011-05-26 23:45:08', '2011-05-26 11:45:08', '<p>This <a title="visit elisacachero.com - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://elisacachero.com">portfolio site</a> is for multi-disciplinary designer Elisa Cachero, and shows her design work in textiles, art direction, print &amp;&nbsp;web design, and event planning.</p>\r\n<p>It uses the Wordpress engine with the popular portfolio theme <a title="autofocus pro demo - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://fthrwght.com/autofocus/plusdemo/">Autofocuspro</a> . Urban Legend web was contracted via <a title="visit wpqestions.com - opens in new window" target="newone" href="http://wpquestions.com">wpquestions.com</a> to update that theme so that;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>the front page displays in the way usually used for category pages</li>\r\n    <li>the number of posts shown beneath the feature image on the home page is limited</li>\r\n    <li>copyright information can be included on single post <a title="example of a single post page using a slider with copyright information" target="newone" href="http://www.elisacachero.com/282/textile_product/product/marie-clutch/">pages</a> which use the JQuery image slider</li>\r\n    <li>the default ''next'' and ''previous'' post arrows on the front page are hidden</li>\r\n    <li>show front-page post titles only on mouse hover</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Via the wpqestions.com site, I''ve now worked on a number of Wordpress autofocuspro installations, and invite <a title="Contact Us" href="http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/contact/">further queries</a> relating to that theme.</p>', 'ElisaCachero.com', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '590-revision-7', '', '', '2011-05-26 23:45:08', '2011-05-26 11:45:08', '', 590, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2011/05/590-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(882, 1, '2012-01-21 13:48:35', '2012-01-21 01:48:35', '<p>This <a target="newone" title="visit Feathers Planning - opens in new window / tab" href="http://feathersplanning.co.nz">site</a> is for a Hamilton-based town-planning consultancy.</p>\r\n<p>It is built on the WordPress platform, using a theme custom-coded by Urban Legend web based on designs from <a target="newone" title="Cube Media - opens in new window / tab" href="http://www.box.co.nz/">Cube Media</a>.</p>\r\n<p>It uses a left-side horizontal menu customised with jQuery, and links section at page bottom controlled by customised widgets.</p>', 'Feathers Planning', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '868-revision-3', '', '', '2012-01-21 13:48:35', '2012-01-21 01:48:35', '', 868, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/868-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(883, 1, '2012-01-16 13:18:21', '2012-01-16 01:18:21', '<p>This site was designed and coded by Urban Legend web, and hosted at</p>\r\n<p><a title="easinet - web page hosting made easy" target="newone" href="http://www.easi.net.nz/web/">Easinet</a></p>\r\n<p>. It re-launched recently using a customised version of the</p>\r\n<p><a target="newone" title="WeBid - opens in new window" href="http://www.webidsupport.com/">WeBid</a></p>\r\n<p>auction engine. This allows the owner to showcase his own stamps, and via a private admin area to manage other users who can also list their stamps.</p>\r\n<p>It features more than 300 stamps for sale from all over the world, and specialises in African stamps.</p>\r\n<p>The WeBid engine is coded in PHP&nbsp;and MySQL.</p>', 'Philactica', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '149-revision-4', '', '', '2012-01-16 13:18:21', '2012-01-16 01:18:21', '', 149, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2012/01/149-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(884, 1, '2010-09-01 00:08:04', '2010-08-31 12:08:04', '<p>This site is for a plastering contract company covering the Bay of Plenty and Waikato areas.</p>\r\n<p>It uses flash animation, as well as an image gallery, to showcase some of the company''s work.</p>\r\n<p>The site is built using the Wordpress engine, and the design is by Urban Legend web, based on the <a href="http://themes.jestro.com/titan/" target="_blank" title="visit the theme author''s site - opens in new window">Titan theme</a>.</p>', 'Lumena Plaster', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '116-revision-2', '', '', '2010-09-01 00:08:04', '2010-08-31 12:08:04', '', 116, 'http://urbanlegendweb.co.nz/2010/09/116-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
